{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be minimalist and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Redstone Realty</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #CC0000;\n            --secondary-color: #E6B3B3;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #F9F9F9;\n            --white: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--white);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #CC0000 3px solid;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x400/CC0000/FFFFFF?text=Welcome+to+Redstone+Realty') no-repeat 0 -400px; /* Placeholder image, adjust path as needed */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--white);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); /* Overlay for better text readability */\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n            max-width: 600px;\n        }\n\n        #properties .property {\n            display: flex;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            background-color: var(--white);\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #properties .property:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        #properties .property-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            min-height: 200px;\n        }\n\n        #properties .property-details {\n            flex: 2;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #properties .property-details h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        #properties .property-details p {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--white);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--white);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            #properties .property {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            #properties .property-image {\n                width: 100%;\n                min-height: 150px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Redstone Realty</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Dream Home Awaits</h2>\n            <p>Discover exceptional properties with a touch of elegance. We're here to guide you every step of the way.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Redstone Realty is a premier real estate brokerage dedicated to providing unparalleled service and expertise. We specialize in connecting buyers and sellers with the perfect properties, ensuring a smooth and rewarding experience.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"properties\">\n            <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n            <div class=\"property\">\n                <div class=\"property-image\" style=\"background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/CC0000/FFFFFF?text=Modern+Villa');\"></div>\n                <div class=\"property-details\">\n                    <h3>Modern Villa in the Hills</h3>\n                    <p>A stunning contemporary villa offering breathtaking views, luxurious amenities, and state-of-the-art design. Features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a private pool, and expansive living spaces.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"property\">\n                <div class=\"property-image\" style=\"background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/CC0000/FFFFFF?text=City+Apartment');\"></div>\n                <div class=\"property-details\">\n                    <h3>Chic City Apartment</h3>\n                    <p>Located in the heart of the city, this stylish apartment boasts modern finishes, a spacious layout, and unparalleled access to urban amenities. Perfect for the discerning city dweller.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"property\">\n                <div class=\"property-image\" style=\"background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/CC0000/FFFFFF?text=Suburban+Family+Home');\"></div>\n                <div class=\"property-details\">\n                    <h3>Suburban Family Home</h3>\n                    <p>A charming and spacious family home in a sought-after neighborhood. Offers a large backyard, a modern kitchen, ample bedrooms, and is close to excellent schools and parks.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>Ready to find your next home or looking to sell? Get in touch with our expert team today.</p>\n            <p>Email: info@redstonerealty.com</p>\n            <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Redstone Realty. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}